OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FAmbulance services will be
OL,7,Fsignificantly impacted by industrial
OL,8,Faction this week, the Health Service
OL,9,FExecutive (HSE) has warned.
OL,11,FThe organisation said the public
OL,12,Fshould still call emergency services
OL,13,Fif urgent medical care is needed.
OL,15,FMembers of the Siptu and Unite unions
OL,16,Fare to impose work-to-rule action on
OL,17,FMonday and a 24-hour stoppage on
OL,18,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
