OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778475896
OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FIn a statement, the HSE said: "During
OL,7,Fthe rolling industrial actions, the
OL,8,Fcapacity of the National Ambulance
OL,9,FService (NAS) to respond will be
OL,10,Fsignificantly impacted."
OL,12,FUnder contingency plans the 999 phone
OL,13,Fservice will be fully operational and
OL,14,Fpriority will be given to patients
OL,15,Fexperiencing emergencies like heart
OL,16,Fattacks or with serious injuries from
OL,17,Froad accidents.
OL,19,FThe HSE said there will be delays in
OL,20,Fresponding to non-life-threatening
OL,21,Fcalls.
OL,26,@nD@_OUrD@XO]
