OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778475896
OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FLast month, ambulance personnel with
OL,7,Fthe unions voted in favour of
OL,8,Findustrial action.
OL,10,FIt will involve members working as
OL,11,Femergency medical technicians (EMTs),
OL,12,Fparamedics, advanced paramedics,
OL,13,Fparamedic specialists and paramedic
OL,14,Fsupervisors.
OL,16,FThey say it is as a result of a
OL,17,Ffailure to implement the
OL,18,Frecommendations of a 2020 report which
OL,19,Flooked at changes to the roles of
OL,20,Fambulance workers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778475896
OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FThe unions say qualifications,
OL,7,Fclinical responsibilities and
OL,8,Foperational duties of personnel have
OL,9,Fexpanded significantly over the last
OL,10,Ftwo decades.
OL,12,FUnite said the Roles and
OL,13,FResponsibilities Review "recommended
OL,14,Fenhanced pay scales to reflect the
OL,15,Fgrowing professionalisation of the
OL,16,Fservice" but "those recommendations
OL,17,Fhave not been implemented".
