OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FThe organisation's general secretary
OL,7,FSharon Gaham said: "It is scandalous
OL,8,Fthat these frontline workers have been
OL,9,Fwaiting for six years for their skills
OL,10,Fand expertise to be recognised."
OL,12,FSiptu's ambulance sector organiser,
OL,13,FJohn McCamley, said: "Members have
OL,14,Fbeen left with no option but to issue
OL,15,Fa strike notice due to this long-
OL,16,Frunning dispute."
OL,26,@oD@TOUrD@`O]uD@VOUxD@QO]
