OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778475896
OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FHe added that the industrial action is
OL,7,F"an indication of the depth of feeling
OL,8,Fwithin the service that their
OL,9,Fsacrifice and commitment over the last
OL,10,F20 years to the professionalisation
OL,11,Fand modernisation of the service have
OL,12,Fbeen forgotten about by the HSE".
OL,14,FThe HSE said it "regrets" the unions'
OL,15,Fdecision to take industrial action and
OL,16,Fhas engaged "intensively" with them
OL,17,Fwith the involvement of the Workplace
OL,18,FRelations Commission (WRC).
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]vD@QOUvD@YO]xD@MOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
