CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778475896
OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FThey said proposals aimed at resolving
OL,7,Fthe dispute were recommended to
OL,8,Fmembers by both unions.
OL,10,FAccording to the HSE, proposals
OL,11,Fincluded 3-14% pay improvements, on
OL,12,Ftop of a 9.25% increase under the 2024-
OL,13,F2026 Public Sector Pay Agreement.
OL,15,FThe service said that in September
OL,16,F2025 it was informed by the two unions
OL,17,Fthat the proposals had been rejected
OL,18,Fby their members.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
