PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778475896
OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FThe HSE also said that between 2022
OL,7,Fand 2025 NAS was the focus of "a major
OL,8,Ftransformation and investment
OL,9,Fprogramme".
OL,11,FIt said while the HSE and the
OL,12,FGovernment accept "the need to both
OL,13,Fincrease and modernise pay
OL,14,Farrangements" for ambulance staff they
OL,15,Fare "also obliged to ensure that in
OL,16,Fexchange for significant increases in
OL,17,Fpay, our services can continue to
OL,18,Ftransform to meet the needs of the
OL,19,Fpublic".
OL,26,@oD@_OUqD@JO]tD@SOUvD@MO]wD@EOU{D@GO]
