OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778475896
OL,3,CAmbulance strike will significantly
OL,4,Cimpact services, HSE warns
OL,6,FThe unions have planned more strikes
OL,7,Fif the dispute is not resolved.
OL,9,FSiptu has said a 48-hour strike is
OL,10,Fbeing organised for May 19, a 72-hour
OL,11,Fone for May 26 and further action for
OL,12,FJune.
OL,14,FThe HSE said other health services
OL,15,Fwill operate normally during the
OL,16,Findustrial action and patients will be
OL,17,Fcontacted if there are any changes to
OL,18,Ftheir planned care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
